ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the United Nations Act
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE UNITED NATIONS ACT in order to (1) harmonize terms used in United Nations Act (UNA) regulations with those used in the enabling statute or across the UNA regulations; (2) add clarity to regulatory provisions as suggested by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations; (3) correct typographical or grammatical errors; (4) repeal obsolete or spent regulatory provisions which have no current application; and (5) update references to United Nations Security Council Resolutions.
